      @Nullable public @Nullable Guild getGuild()

      Returns:

    • getInteractionData

      @Nullable public @Nullable InteractionData getInteractionData()
      Returns the interaction data that was created from the event. This can be used by the end user, but is not recommended.

      Note: Will return null if getInteractionType() is InteractionType.PING

      Returns:
      InteractionData object containing the interaction data.
